{"tid":542062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊一條法例話香港法定語言係粵語同英文?","createTime":"2018-01-27T06:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T10:22:58.000Z","uid":106675,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b72c8cc3d2ac2aabb2e7393619ab72eb3c00fe56","tid":542062,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"幾個post都見到有人話英文係香港&quot;法定語言&quot;, 所以考英文係合理, 普通話唔係<br />\n<br />\n我只係搵到:<br />\n<br />\n基本法第九條<br />\n香港特別行政區的行政機關、立法機關和司法機關，<span style=\"color: red;\">除使用中文外，還可使用英文，英文也是正式語文。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港得法定語文(口語+文字), 冇所謂法定語言(口語)<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個point係invalid"},{"pid":"d7cf2a85a70b646bbd855de16ffe659013aeeaa0","tid":542062,"uid":14758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b72c8cc3d2ac2aabb2e7393619ab72eb3c00fe56","tid":542062,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"幾個post都見到有人話英文係香港&quot;法定語言&quot;, 所以考英文係合理, 普通話唔係<br />\n<br />\n我只係搵到:<br />\n<br />\n基本法第九條<br />\n香港特別行政區的行政機關、立法機關和司法機關，<span style=\"color: red;\">除使用中文外，還可使用英文，英文也是正式語文。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港得法定語文(口語+文字), 冇所謂法定語言(口語)<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個point係invalid"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講語文=口語+文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e27dbc1156360b4a8c13caae71812468d612ff","tid":542062,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45e82e43dfc66d123491b9c9380d8ca440f3641","tid":542062,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6e27dbc1156360b4a8c13caae71812468d612ff","tid":542062,"uid":14758,"lik